data.description:
Great opportunity with one of the largest townhomes in Woodbury!  This home features a large main level
master suite with huge walk in closet.  Upstairs you'll find two nice sized bedrooms, loft and full
bathroom.  Massive lower level is perfect for entertaining!  Incredible amount of space for this price!  Conveniently located off of Bailey Road near grocery, schools and restaurants.  Quick freeway access makes your drive to work a breeze!  Welcome home!
